{"word":"Ezekiel","slug":"ezekiel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ezekiel</b> <a href=\"#/H3168\">H3168</a> <br/> A priest.<br/> Time of his prophecy<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=1&verse=3'>Eze 1:3</a><br/> Persecution of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=3&verse=25'>Eze 3:25</a><br/> Visions of:<br/> - God's glory<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=1'>Eze 1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=8'>Eze 8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=10'>Eze 10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=11&verse=22'>Eze 11:22</a> <br/> - Jews abominations<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=8&verse=6'>Eze 8:6</a> <br/> - Their punishment<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=9&verse=10'>Eze 9:10</a> <br/> - The valley of dry bones<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=37&verse=14'>Eze 37:14</a> <br/> - A man with measuring line<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=40'>Eze 40</a> <br/> - The river<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=47&verse=5'>Eze 47:5</a> <br/> Teaches by pantomime:<br/> - Teaches by pantomime:<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=3&verse=26'>Eze 3:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=24&verse=27'>Eze 24:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=33&verse=22'>Eze 33:22</a> <br/> - Symbolizes the siege of Jerusalem by drawings on a tile<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=4'>Eze 4</a> <br/> - Shaves himself<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=5&verse=4'>Eze 5:4</a> <br/> - Removes his stuff to illustrate the approaching Jewish captivity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=12&verse=7'>Eze 12:7</a> <br/> - Sighs<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=21&verse=7'>Eze 21:7</a> <br/> - Employs a boiling pot to symbolize the destruction of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=24&verse=14'>Eze 24:14</a> <br/> - Omits mourning at the death of his wife<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=24&verse=27'>Eze 24:27</a> <br/> - Prophesies by parable of an eagle<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=17&verse=10'>Eze 17:10</a> <br/> - Other parables<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=15'>Eze 15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=19&verse=14'>Eze 19:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=23'>Eze 23</a> <br/> Prophecies of:<br/> - Concerning various nations<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=25'>Eze 25</a> <br/> - His popularity<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=33&verse=32'>Eze 33:32</a> "}]}